title: Maybe (Itaewon Class OST part 7)
lyrics: Maybe your smile is the only thing that I want for now In the end I’m gonna want something more, I know Just the two of us we walk along and staring into the eyes Maybe it’s the only thing that we need for now Underneath the moonlight, a full of silvery light Can you take me there if it’s okay with you? A part of my mind whis pers to your heart Now this is the moment to realize Just say every thing you want from me I’ll still be here Just say everything you want from me
